17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你该来听 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 西方哲学初学者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 逻辑思维训练爱好者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 理性主义者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 旧世界的批判者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 渴望更加了解自我和世界的探索者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret