思想实验二：消失的蓝色色块和玛丽的房间｜我们到底知道什么？

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app1PqfnDec5369/a_5c343a4c0f456_bvq5ZvkZ

<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/15036600_1545795997.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="思想实验-04.jpg" style="text-align: center;"/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>哲学学习有捷径吗？</strong><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">作为科学中的科学，在很多人的印象里哲学是一门艰深晦涩、让人皓首穷经的玄学。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">但是有一种方法可以让你迅速get哲学思考的魅力，这就是思想实验。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>什么是思想实验？</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">哲学家们依靠丰富的想象力、用逻辑的方法建构一个故事场景。在这个场景中，我们能够进行一些在现实生活中无法做到的行为，预料这些行为导致的一种或者几种可能的情况，借此来阐明抽象的哲学概念、检验哲学理论。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>知识的革命和世界的改变，往往诞生于大胆的狂想与高妙的假设中，</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>每一个伟大的思想实验，都会引发深刻的思考乃至洞察。</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">我们甄选了最具生命力的十五个思想实验，去反思时间、空间、自我、理性、正义……等等哲学中最重要的概念。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">在大多数时间里，我们对于这些最基本的观念和想法不假思索，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">按照约定俗成、显而易见的方式去理解和实践，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>而哲学恰恰是要挑战这种态度。</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>借由这些思想实验我们一起检验那些人生中最基本的、最习以为常的想法，</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">用一次思想的探险，抽丝剥茧、深度解读与我们每一个人息息相关的重大问题。<br/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/54270100_1545795997.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="思想实验-06.jpg"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 为你开启人类思想的实验室 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/95337200_1545795997.jpg"/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17p