nherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;大开的脑洞、与哲学分析相伴随的人类超级想象力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;运用思想实验检验理论的能力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;对你用来组织经验、引导决策的信念和价值的反思</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;合乎逻辑的论证与不合逻辑的论证之间的不同为你开启人类思想的实验室</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你该来听 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 西方哲学初学者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 逻辑思维训练爱好者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 理性主义者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 旧世界的批判者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;●&nbsp; 渴望更加了解自我和世界的探索者</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret