思想实验七：公地问题和孔多塞悖论｜我们可以理性的选择吗？

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app1S9tNjYQ1820/a_5c343a4c0f2b9_jHupgAaS

<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/15036600_1545795997.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="思想实验-04.jpg" style="text-align: center;"/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>哲学学习有捷径吗？</strong><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">作为科学中的科学，在很多人的印象里哲学是一门艰深晦涩、让人皓首穷经的玄学。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">但是有一种方法可以让你迅速get哲学思考的魅力，这就是思想实验。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>什么是思想实验？</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">哲学家们依靠丰富的想象力、用逻辑的方法建构一个故事场景。在这个场景中，我们能够进行一些在现实生活中无法做到的行为，预料这些行为导致的一种或者几种可能的情况，借此来阐明抽象的哲学概念、检验哲学理论。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>知识的革命和世界的改变，往往诞生于大胆的狂想与高妙的假设中，</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>每一个伟大的思想实验，都会引发深刻的思考乃至洞察。</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">我们甄选了最具生命力的十五个思想实验，去反思时间、空间、自我、理性、正义……等等哲学中最重要的概念。</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">在大多数时间里，我们对于这些最基本的观念和想法不假思索，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">按照约定俗成、显而易见的方式去理解和实践，</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>而哲学恰恰是要挑战这种态度。</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><strong>借由这些思想实验我们一起检验那些人生中最基本的、最习以为常的想法，</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">用一次思想的探险，抽丝剥茧、深度解读与我们每一个人息息相关的重大问题。<br/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/54270100_1545795997.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="思想实验-06.jpg"/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 为你开启人类思想的实验室 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><br/></h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/95337200_1545795997.jpg"/><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 你将获得 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;哲学家的超级思维工具箱</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;颠覆固有认知、破除思维枷锁的思维训练</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;时间、空间、自我等西方哲学核心概念和基本问题的深刻解读</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;迫近事物本质的有效思考能力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;西方哲学史的入门知识，哲学各个分支领域的识别能力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;用逻辑思维考察事物的方法</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;大开的脑洞、与哲学分析相伴随的人类超级想象力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;运用思想实验检验理论的能力</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;对你用来组织经验、引导决策的信念和价值的反思</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;">&nbsp;&nbsp;● &nbsp;合乎逻辑的论证与不合逻辑的论证之间的不同为你开启人类思想的实验室</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 